item.title: Analysing my university's publications
item.description: Hello! I have recently finished my master’s degree and finished my summer projects! With spare time on my hands, I have finally gotten around to analysing the full list of my university’s publications. I have run into this dataset during a seminar about InCites, a tool for researchers to look into their university’s research, collaborations with other universities and even funding…
